OL,5, Rishi Sunak has apologised for the     
OL,6, historical treatment of LGBT veterans  
OL,7, who were sacked or forced out of the   
OL,8, military for being gay.                
OL,10,FThe PM called the ban an "appalling    
OL,11,Ffailure" of the British state.         
OL,13,FIt was illegal to be gay in the British
OL,14,Fmilitary until 2000 - with thousands of
OL,15,Fveterans thought to be affected.       
OL,17,FA report into their treatment          
OL,18,Frecommended they be given a financial  
OL,19,Freward and that the PM publicly        
OL,20,Fapologise.                             
